WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.370 --> 00:00:03.259
Does it bother you to see my son?

2
00:00:03.259 --> 00:00:08.929
Not anymore, but how do you plan on introducing me?

3
00:00:08.929 --> 00:00:11.089
Do you remember the terms of our deal?

4
00:00:11.089 --> 00:00:18.379
Ethan, can I go and visit my stepmom?

5
00:00:18.379 --> 00:00:22.699
Charlotte's really worried about me. I'll make it back in that villa party.

6
00:00:22.699 --> 00:00:26.309
Of course. You're not a prisoner.

7
00:00:26.309 --> 00:00:40.390
Chloe? I did not expect to see you here.

8
00:00:40.390 --> 00:00:43.390
I've missed you so much. Where have you been?

9
00:00:43.390 --> 00:00:47.670
Oh, look. This is my best friend Vivian.

10
00:00:47.670 --> 00:00:49.670
Vivian, this is Sister Foster.

11
00:00:49.670 --> 00:00:51.670
I know. Heard a lot about you.

12
00:00:51.670 --> 00:00:54.859
Why didn't you tell me you were friends with Mr. Foster?

13
00:00:54.859 --> 00:00:57.859
I don't know if Chloe would call us friends.

